{"chunk_id": "doc_quartz#chunk_001", "doc_id": "doc_quartz", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "quartz", "page": null, "source": "PubChem Quartz", "text": "石英是常见的硅酸盐矿物，主要化学成分是二氧化硅 SiO2。", "topic": "concept", "url": "https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/Quartz"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_quartz#chunk_002", "doc_id": "doc_quartz", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "quartz", "page": null, "source": "PubMed quartz Raman heating study", "text": "石英常见强拉曼峰接近 464 cm-1，可作为识别石英的重要光谱证据。", "topic": "spectroscopy", "url": "https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14658655/"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_quartz#chunk_003", "doc_id": "doc_quartz", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "quartz", "page": null, "source": "Britannica mineral hardness", "text": "石英硬度通常高于方解石，适合与碳酸盐矿物做性质对比。", "topic": "mineral_property", "url": "https://www.britannica.com/science/mineral-chemical-compound/Hardness"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_feldspar#chunk_001", "doc_id": "doc_feldspar", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "feldspar", "page": null, "source": "PubChem Feldspar", "text": "长石是一类铝硅酸盐框架矿物，常见于火成岩和变质岩。", "topic": "mineral_property", "url": "https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/Feldspar"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_feldspar#chunk_002", "doc_id": "doc_feldspar", "license": "public_use_permitted", "mineral": "feldspar", "page": null, "source": "NASA NTRS feldspar Raman characterization", "text": "长石与石英同属硅酸盐体系，部分框架振动特征可能接近，弱峰和噪声会增加混淆风险。", "topic": "spectroscopy", "url": "https://ntrs.nasa.gov/citations/20030111413"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_calcite#chunk_001", "doc_id": "doc_calcite", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "calcite", "page": null, "source": "PubChem Calcite", "text": "方解石是典型碳酸盐矿物，不属于硅酸盐矿物。", "topic": "concept", "url": "https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/Calcite"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_calcite#chunk_002", "doc_id": "doc_calcite", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "calcite", "page": null, "source": "RSC sulfated calcium carbonates Raman study", "text": "方解石的碳酸根特征带常接近 1085 cm-1，可用于与石英区分。", "topic": "spectroscopy", "url": "https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlelanding/1997/an/a606167b"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_calcite#chunk_003", "doc_id": "doc_calcite", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "calcite", "page": null, "source": "Britannica Calcite", "text": "方解石硬度低于石英，且遇稀盐酸常发生起泡反应。", "topic": "mineral_property", "url": "https://www.britannica.com/science/calcite"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_hematite#chunk_001", "doc_id": "doc_hematite", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "hematite", "page": null, "source": "PubChem Hematite", "text": "赤铁矿是铁氧化物矿物，不是硅酸盐矿物，也不是碳酸盐矿物。", "topic": "concept", "url": "https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/Hematite-_Fe2O3"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_hematite#chunk_002", "doc_id": "doc_hematite", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "hematite", "page": null, "source": "Britannica Hematite", "text": "赤铁矿谱图常体现铁氧化物相关特征，可用于解释铁氧化物样本识别。", "topic": "spectroscopy", "url": "https://www.britannica.com/science/hematite"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_spectroscopy#chunk_001", "doc_id": "doc_spectroscopy", "license": "public_use_permitted", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "NASA NTRS Raman point-count method", "text": "光谱证据通过峰位、特征带和峰形支持矿物识别，也可用于分析分类混淆。", "topic": "spectroscopy", "url": "https://ntrs.nasa.gov/citations/19980021297"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_spectroscopy#chunk_003", "doc_id": "doc_spectroscopy", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "PMC Raman hyperspectral pitfalls", "text": "单个弱峰可能受噪声、基线漂移或其他矿物峰重叠影响，证据不足时不应给出确定结论。", "topic": "spectroscopy", "url": "https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC3807534/"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_system#chunk_001", "doc_id": "doc_system", "license": "internal_project_note", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "MiniGeo system design notes", "text": "RAG 回答返回 chunk id 可以让答案证据来源可追踪，便于检查引用是否支持结论。", "topic": "system", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/system-citations"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_system#chunk_002", "doc_id": "doc_system", "license": "internal_project_note", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "MiniGeo system design notes", "text": "公开资料进入语料库时应记录 URL 和 license，以控制来源追踪和版权风险。", "topic": "system", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/data-license"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_system#chunk_003", "doc_id": "doc_system", "license": "internal_project_note", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "MiniGeo system design notes", "text": "Benchmark reference answer 不应直接作为 SFT 输出训练，以降低 benchmark 泄漏风险。", "topic": "system", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/leakage"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_system#chunk_004", "doc_id": "doc_system", "license": "internal_project_note", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "MiniGeo system design notes", "text": "MiniGeo 的贡献是 benchmark、RAG、证据验证和数据分析闭环，而不是训练新的地学基础模型。", "topic": "system", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/positioning"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_system#chunk_005", "doc_id": "doc_system", "license": "internal_project_note", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "MiniGeo system design notes", "text": "失败案例分析应区分数据缺失、检索失败、生成错误、验证误判和 SQL 错误。", "topic": "system", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/failure-analysis"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_system#chunk_006", "doc_id": "doc_system", "license": "internal_project_note", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "MiniGeo system design notes", "text": "Agent 最终答案同时返回 SQL 和证据，可以提高结构化数据结论和地学解释的可追踪性。", "topic": "system", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/agent-report"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_system#chunk_007", "doc_id": "doc_system", "license": "internal_project_note", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "MiniGeo system design notes", "text": "Verifier 的 supported 表示 claim 被证据支持，insufficient_evidence 表示当前证据不足以支持回答或 claim。", "topic": "system", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/verifier-labels"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_system#chunk_008", "doc_id": "doc_system", "license": "internal_project_note", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "MiniGeo system design notes", "text": "QLoRA 应在 benchmark 和 RAG 稳定后进行，否则无法判断微调是否真正提升可靠性。", "topic": "system", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/sft-order"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_system#chunk_009", "doc_id": "doc_system", "license": "internal_project_note", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "MiniGeo system design notes", "text": "混合检索结合词项匹配和语义匹配，预期比单一 BM25 有更高证据召回率。", "topic": "system", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/hybrid-retrieval"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_system#chunk_010", "doc_id": "doc_system", "license": "internal_project_note", "mineral": "", "page": null, "source": "MiniGeo system design notes", "text": "Latency 是系统可用性评估的一部分，反映端到端响应成本。", "topic": "system", "url": "https://example.org/minigeo/latency"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_dolomite#chunk_001", "doc_id": "doc_dolomite", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "dolomite", "page": null, "source": "PubChem Dolomite", "text": "白云石是钙镁碳酸盐矿物，常用化学式为 CaMg(CO3)2。", "topic": "concept", "url": "https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/Dolomite"}
{"chunk_id": "doc_dolomite#chunk_002", "doc_id": "doc_dolomite", "license": "source_metadata_only", "mineral": "dolomite", "page": null, "source": "Geology.com carbonate acid test", "text": "白云石与方解石同属碳酸盐体系，但含有镁，反应和谱学解释需要区分。", "topic": "mineral_property", "url": "https://geology.com/minerals/acid-test.shtml"}
